				<div class="faq">
					<h4>I am not computer savvy; Can you design a custom artwork for me?</h4>
					<p>Absolutely, we have Desingers in house that will make your dreams come true, you just need to image it and we'll make it happen. The best part is that we don't charge extra for this service!</p>
				</div><!-- faq -->
				<div class="faq">
					<h4>What type of chocolate do you use?</h4>
					<p>We use the finest Belgian Chocolate in virtually all of our products.</p>
				</div><!-- faq -->
				<div class="faq">
					<h4>How long does it take to get my order?</h4>
					<p>All Standard non-personalized items will ship within 3 days, while custom orders will be ready for shipment in 2 weeks or less.</p>
				</div><!-- faq -->
				<div class="faq">
					<h4>How long will the chocolate last?</h4>
					<p>Our chocolate products have a shelf life of 8 months to 1 year. We do not recommend refrigeration. Simply store the product at room temperature (not over 74*) - keep away from direct sunlight and heating units.</p>
				</div><!-- faq -->
				<div class="faq">
					<h4>Is your chocolate Kosher?</h4>
					<p>Yes, products are OU-D certified Kosher Dairy. Parve chocolate available upon request for some products.</p>
				</div><!-- faq -->
				<div class="faq">
					<h4>What forms of payment do you accept?</h4>
					<p>Online orders must be placed using a credit card. We also accept purchase orders for orders over $250.00.</p>
				</div><!-- faq -->
				<div class="faq">
					<h4>How do I know my chocolate won't melt?</h4>
					<p>We use gel ice packs and insulated boxes in the warm months to keep the product cold until delivery. 2-day or overnight shipping may be required during warm months.</p>
